# 🔟 Numerical Practice

### Given

| Process | AT | BT |
| ------- | -: | -: |
| P1      |  0 |  6 |
| P2      |  1 |  2 |
| P3      |  2 |  4 |

**Question:** Draw the Gantt Chart using **SRTF**.

### Solution

* 0–1 : P1
* 1–3 : P2 (preempts P1)
* 3–7 : P3
* 7–12 : P1

```text
0   1   3   7   12
|P1|P2|P3|P1|
```

